2026-01-10  Michael Herstine  <sp1ff@pobox.com>

	Cut release 0.2.1

	s/valueset!/valueset_all!/
	Our unit tests rely on the undocumented `tracing` macro `valueset!`.
	`tracing` 0.1.44 (December 18, 2025) introduced a breaking change
	to this macro. This commit moves us to the the also undocumented
	`valueset_all!` macro which now works.

